{"id":118847,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/11/简讯：李登辉称台湾人应拜靖国-2/","date":"2010-11-02T01:07:35Z","modified":"2010-11-02T01:07:35Z","title":"简讯：李登辉称台湾人应拜靖国","content":"<div>\n<p>日本前首相安倍晋三访问台湾拜会前总统李登辉时谈及靖国神社议题。</p>\n<p>据台湾《联合报》报道，李登辉肯定安倍到忠烈祠致意，他认为台湾人到日本靖国神社，也应该鞠躬一下，“这是尊重彼此国家”。</p>\n<p>李登辉强调，安倍此行主要是处理台湾与日本的交通问题，松山羽田通航，让台湾与日本变成一日生活圈，一天八个班次，有些人结束东京的工作，就可飞回台北，将来台湾与日本做生意会很方便。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/CKhPQk30BT9EfSrU1zsGvv0D2A8/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/CKhPQk30BT9EfSrU1zsGvv0D2A8/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/CKhPQk30BT9EfSrU1zsGvv0D2A8/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/CKhPQk30BT9EfSrU1zsGvv0D2A8/1/di\"></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=zP8Nt-5RjYQ:auk6MuyIjk4:mqyYa2mfVbY\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=mqyYa2mfVbY\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=zP8Nt-5RjYQ:auk6MuyIjk4:PFx2F_oWK34\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=PFx2F_oWK34\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=zP8Nt-5RjYQ:auk6MuyIjk4:DUWcskeyX7o\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=DUWcskeyX7o\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=zP8Nt-5RjYQ:auk6MuyIjk4:clraHZBW0_I\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=clraHZBW0_I\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=zP8Nt-5RjYQ:auk6MuyIjk4:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=zP8Nt-5RjYQ:auk6MuyIjk4:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" /></a>\n</div>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/zP8Nt-5RjYQ\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p>请看原文：<br />\n<a target=\"_blan